# SEOBlogBot Environment Configuration

# =============================================================================
# Google Search Console API (Required for check-indexing-status tool)
# =============================================================================

# Option 1: Path to service account JSON key file (recommended)
GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS=/path/to/your-service-account-key.json

# Option 2: Inline credentials (for cloud deployments)
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_EMAIL=your-service-account@your-project.iam.gserviceaccount.com
# GOOGLE_PRIVATE_KEY="-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----\n...\n-----END PRIVATE KEY-----"

# =============================================================================
# PageSpeed Insights API (Optional - for higher rate limits)
# =============================================================================

# Get your API key at: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
# Without a key: 25,000 queries/day limit (usually sufficient)
# PAGESPEED_API_KEY=your-pagespeed-api-key
